Interface BareJsonBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IndentedJsonBuilder, JsonBuilder, JsonStructureBuilder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBareJsonBuilder, MiniJsonBuilder, SimpleJsonBuilder

    public interface BareJsonBuilder
extends IndentedJsonBuilder, JsonStructureBuilder
    Base JSON string builder interface (which uses only Map and List). This is the primary base interface for MiniJson JSON builder implementations.
